  "description": "The spring reverb has become the primary instrument. It resonates of its own accord — metallic, liquid, ancient. Send amount at maximum pushes every note into the spring's long sympathetic decay. The oscillator provides only the initial strike. B004 at its theological extreme: the metallic splash as entire sonic world.",
